{% doc %}
  Cart Drawer

  Renders the cart drawer component as a slide-out panel.
  The primary cart drawer implementation lives inline in snippets/header-actions.liquid,
  which renders the full cart-drawer-component when settings.cart_type == 'drawer'.

  This snippet is rendered from layout/theme.liquid as a fallback entry point.
  It is intentionally a no-op because header-actions.liquid already renders the
  cart drawer within the header section group. Adding duplicate markup here would
  cause double-rendering of the drawer.

  The cart drawer features:
  - Slide-out panel with cart line items via cart-products snippet
  - Quantity controls and item removal
  - Cart summary with subtotal and checkout CTA
  - Empty cart state with continue shopping link
  - Auto-open on add-to-cart when enabled
  - Keyboard accessible (Escape to close, focus trap)

  @example {% render 'cart-drawer' %}
{% enddoc %}

{% comment %}
